<i>[You Are Desire]</i>

18
00:01:29,818 --> 00:01:33,696
<i>[Episode 15: Daydream For You]</i>

19
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:38,359
Wait. Hold on.

20
00:01:38,359 --> 00:01:39,439
Keep our relationship a secret?

21
00:01:39,439 --> 00:01:43,920
Do you mean that we can't hold hands and…

22
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:47,000
Of course not. We just can't do that at school.

23
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:48,719
But we can do whatever we want in private.

24
00:01:52,879 --> 00:01:54,840
If you keep being silent,
I'll take it as a yes.

25
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:57,159
But there has to be a time limit, right?

26
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:58,599
We can't always be like this.

27
00:01:58,599 --> 00:02:01,280
We won't. She just broke up.

28
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,799
She'll be fine after a period.

29
00:02:02,799 --> 00:02:04,079
By then, we'll tell her about us.

30
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:07,959
<i>Don't worry. I won't keep you waiting for long.</i>

31
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,592
Bye.

32
00:02:33,319 --> 00:02:35,000
Why don't you have any classes on Wednesday?

33
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,759
Do you want to take a day off?

34
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:38,199
Well, I wish.

35
00:02:38,199 --> 00:02:40,680
My dad asked me to intern at a law firm.

36
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:43,319
He said,
"Theory needs to be combined with practice."

37
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:45,800
I need to take a day off every week to work.

38
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:50,199
Geez, we're only freshmen.
Do you have to push yourself so hard?

39
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:52,960
I didn't want to go either,
but my dad insisted,

40
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:56,080
so I had to agree. At least I can make
some extra money. What about you?

41
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,120
Have you chosen your classes?

42
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:59,360
Not yet. There's still plenty of time.

43
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,680
I need to focus on my important task first.

44
00:03:03,737 --> 00:03:06,759
<i>[School Forum]</i>

45
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:09,120
Are you really going to
post Wenwen's matter on the forum?

46
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,719
Of course.

47
00:03:10,719 --> 00:03:13,080
Before Wenwen went home,
I already got her permission.

48
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:16,280
I want to expose
these scumbags' tricks on the internet.

49
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:19,280
When the other girls read my post,
they'll know better and avoid being hurt.

50
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:22,080
Isn't this a bit too much?
What if it causes a big fuss?

51
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:25,439
Don't worry. I only use fake names.

52
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:28,120
Later, I'll ask Lin Yujing for some advice.

53
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:29,520
I'll also add
some stuff about Shen Juan to my post.

54
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:32,719
And then, no one will know who I refer to.

55
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,199
Why hasn't Lin Yujing come back yet?

56
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:38,360
She's rarely in the dormitory these days.

57
00:03:41,319 --> 00:03:42,400
I'm out of inspiration.

58
00:03:44,159 --> 00:03:46,080
The atmosphere truly has a great impact.

59
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,360
It's my first time
doing something serious in an Internet cafe.

60
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,879
But now I even feel guilty somehow.

61
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:52,520
Well, our university library is much better.

62
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,960
Shall we go back?

63
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:57,280
Nope. Our relationship is still a secret.

64
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,000
Let's stay here
and get it done as quickly as possible.

65
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:08,520
Why so fast?
Are you picking your classes randomly?

66
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,159
No. I know what I've chosen.

67
00:04:12,439 --> 00:04:14,000
What about the public class?

68
00:04:14,592 --> 00:04:15,840
Anything. It's up to you.

69
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:22,279
Up to me? Then I'll pick flower arrangement,
tea art, and jewelry appreciation.

70
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:30,199
Seriously? Aren't you going to think twice?

71
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:33,040
It's fine. I can learn anything.

72
00:04:41,017 --> 00:04:43,005
<i>[Shooting, Rong Huai]</i>

73
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,920
Oh, there's shooting. I want to try it.

74
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,240
Didn't you learn to shoot before?

75
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,240
Do you want to try it?

76
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,800
I…

77
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,879
I'll choose basketball.

78
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,839
Basketball suits you too.

79
00:05:04,879 --> 00:05:07,720
The smell here is too choking.
Shall we go back?

80
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,879
Guys,

81
00:06:13,879 --> 00:06:16,000
this restaurant only uses fresh ingredients.

82
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,319
The owner is a great cook.

83
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:19,680
The skewers he makes taste amazing.

84
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:22,279
Look! It just…

85
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:30,439
What's wrong? No viewers again?

86
00:06:30,439 --> 00:06:31,560
Can you not laugh at me?

87
00:06:32,759 --> 00:06:34,360
Nobody came when I was live-streaming just now.

88
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:37,120
You didn't help me and even laughed at me.

89
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,040
When did you become so fragile?

90
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:41,040
I'm not fragile. It's just…

91
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,360
I'm just too miserable.

92
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:46,480
I remember you didn't pass the CET-4, did you?

93
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,839
I'll try again. I'm just a sophomore.

94
00:06:48,839 --> 00:06:50,199
All right. Don't make yourself look so pitiful.

95
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,560
I can't help you with English,

96
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,319
but I can help you with your account
and see what I can do.

97
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,199
This short video has a decent number of views.

98
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,079
That one? That's because Juan suddenly appeared

99
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:09,639
when I recorded this video.

100
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,600
It's late. Why are you here?

101
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:20,240
He insisted that late-night snack hunting
could attract more viewers.

102
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,079
But there was nobody at all.

103
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:25,120
The food here is good. Want to have a try?

104
00:07:26,079 --> 00:07:27,680
I'll have a beer.

105
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,120
I'll get it for you. Hold on.

106
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:33,399
Have some barbecue.

107
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,079
Come on. Let's drink.

108
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,720
Eat up! Eat up!

109
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,959
Juan, eat up.

110
00:07:53,839 --> 00:07:56,439
Here. It's yours.

111
00:08:00,399 --> 00:08:01,839
What's wrong? Something on your mind?

112
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,600
I got scratched by a cat.

113
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:10,839
Cat? You mean Orange?
Isn't it usually well-behaved?

114
00:08:10,839 --> 00:08:11,920
Why did it scratch you?

115
00:08:13,199 --> 00:08:14,959
Pets are like people.

116
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:17,439
Once they know they're special,
they become arrogant.

117
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:19,680
But you can only spoil it.

118
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,560
After all, that's your cat.
What else can you do?

119
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:27,319
You're right. I still have to spoil her.

120
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,720
Come on. Let's drink!

121
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:58,559
Senior He, what's the matter?

122
00:08:58,559 --> 00:09:01,960
Hello, I-I want to ask you for a favor.

123
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:06,200
<i>I didn't pass the CET-4 in June.</i>

124
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:08,360
My teacher said if I can't pass in December,

125
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,159
I won't be able to participate in
the practical class during the winter vacation.

126
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:12,159
So strict!

127
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:13,960
<i>Isn't it?</i>

128
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:16,600
I never thought that I would still
be ruled by English in university.

129
00:09:17,399 --> 00:09:19,840
But I heard that you did very well
on your college entrance English exam.

130
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:22,519
<i>So, I'm thinking,</i>

131
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:25,759
could you please help me with my English?

132
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,279
I can, but…

133
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:33,080
<i>I haven't passed the CET-4 either.</i>

134
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,200
I need to get prepared.

135
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:39,639
How about this?
I'll go to the university town in a few days.

136
00:09:39,639 --> 00:09:40,919
I'll visit you by then.

137
00:09:40,919 --> 00:09:43,000
Okay. Great! I'll be waiting.

138
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,679
<i>Okay.</i>

139
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:45,984
Okay, bye!

140
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,679
<i>This is one of the old exams.</i>

141
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:58,159
<i>You should go through it,
and I'll get to know your level.</i>

142
00:09:58,159 --> 00:10:00,559
<i>It'll be easier for me to know
which part I should focus on.</i>

143
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,879
<i>Juan, how did you get gossiped about?</i>

144
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:30,639
What gossip?

145
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:33,679
<i>I mean the gossip post on our school forum.</i>

146
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:35,840
<i>Someone posted about you just now.</i>

147
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:38,000
<i>The poster is spreading rumors that
you've dumped your girlfriend.</i>

148
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:41,200
<i>Your first love is mentioned,
but it seems to refer to Lin Yujing.</i>

149
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:43,240
<i>This is pure nonsense, Juan.</i>

150
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:01,320
<i>It seems that
we can't keep our relationship a secret.</i>

151
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:03,240
<i>It gives rumors a chance to spread.</i>

152
00:11:16,799 --> 00:11:19,080
<i>Since it's a rumor, it doesn't matter.</i>

153
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,840
<i>Let's keep the truth between us.</i>

154
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:28,384
Oh, dear. How should we tell her?

155
00:11:28,384 --> 00:11:29,856
No idea.

156
00:11:31,720 --> 00:11:34,320
You're back! Hurry up and get dressed.

157
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:37,279
Tonight the guitar club is having
a welcome party at the beach.

158
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:38,360
Let's go together.

159
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:40,639
Welcome party?

160
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:42,879
Didn't you say that
getting close to men will bring misfortune?

161
00:11:42,879 --> 00:11:45,639
I also said yesterday that
the best way to forget a jerk

162
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:47,240
is to meet your Mr. Right.

163
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:52,799
I'm a bit tired. I just want to have some rest.
You guys have fun.

164
00:11:52,799 --> 00:11:54,080
Wait.

165
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:59,399
Lin Yujing, you must watch this video.

166
00:11:59,399 --> 00:12:00,640
Yes, you must watch it.

167
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:20,159
Well, the camerawork is quite poor.

168
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:24,639
Lin Yujing, wake up! Is that the point?

169
00:12:24,639 --> 00:12:26,039
Did you see those bullet comments?

170
00:12:26,039 --> 00:12:28,200
He is showing off like a peacock!

171
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:30,799
Lin Yujing, since that's the case,

172
00:12:30,799 --> 00:12:32,279
you must prove that you're better than him.

173
00:12:32,279 --> 00:12:34,080
If you lose to him, I will be angry.

174
00:12:34,639 --> 00:12:35,759
Yujing,

175
00:12:36,279 --> 00:12:39,639
will you keep me company? Please?

176
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:40,879
Please?

177
00:12:42,759 --> 00:12:44,000
- Okay.
- Good! We'll go!

178
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,159
I'll use all my make-up techniques on you.

179
00:12:46,159 --> 00:12:48,519
I'll give you the most beautiful makeup
and make you the star of tonight!

180
00:12:48,519 --> 00:12:49,720
After I finish, we will post her on Moments.

181
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,720
Yes! Post her on Moments!

182
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,808
Come on!

183
00:12:51,808 --> 00:12:53,240
T-That's not necessary. Really.

184
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:55,559
It's a bit too much. I'm already pretty.

185
00:12:55,559 --> 00:12:57,200
- Use this one.
- We can't make her seem too cheesy.

186
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,840
- We need to use this one.
- Oh, that looks good.

187
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,559
This place is so beautiful.

188
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:10,639
There are so many handsome guys over there.

189
00:13:10,639 --> 00:13:12,120
Let's go! Hurry!

190
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,320
This place is really beautiful.

191
00:13:14,432 --> 00:13:16,519
Lin Yujing, since you're here,

192
00:13:16,519 --> 00:13:17,840
you have to at least pretend to be happy.

193
00:13:18,799 --> 00:13:22,080
Come. This way!

194
00:13:23,039 --> 00:13:24,360
Wait for us!

195
00:13:26,656 --> 00:13:27,720
Stand in the middle.

196
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:30,440
Then I-I'll join you.

197
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,360
Lin Yujing, give me a smile!

198
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,799
Three, two, one!

199
00:13:34,799 --> 00:13:36,000
Rock and roll!

200
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,679
Good! Give me another pose.

201
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:40,919
Three, two, one, rock and roll!

202
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,480
Thank you.

203
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:46,320
Hey, are you here to join our club?

204
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,552
I…

205
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:51,159
Shall we add each other on WeChat?
I'm the president of the guitar club.

206
00:13:51,159 --> 00:13:52,320
I can give you some detailed information.

207
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:53,960
No need. I…

208
00:13:57,504 --> 00:13:58,919
Okay, okay.

209
00:14:06,039 --> 00:14:08,679
All right. Our performance will start soon.

210
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:09,720
Be sure to come!

211
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,240
Okay, thank you.

212
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:13,480
- Shall we go watch the performance?
- Okay. Let's go.

213
00:14:13,480 --> 00:14:14,600
Lin Yujing, hurry up.

214
00:14:19,039 --> 00:14:20,759
<i>What are you doing, my lady?</i>

215
00:14:28,159 --> 00:14:30,559
<i>I'm at the library. Talk later.</i>

216
00:14:51,159 --> 00:14:52,384
Focus on the performance!

217
00:15:02,745 --> 00:15:08,109
<i>[Post Moments]</i>

218
00:15:12,424 --> 00:15:15,240
<i>[Allow Shen Juan to view]</i>

219
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,639
Why did you let him see your Moments?

220
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:19,080
If not, how can he see those photos?

221
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,720
Brilliant.

222
00:15:34,799 --> 00:15:37,200
<i>Juan, have you seen Gu Xia's Moments?</i>

223
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,679
<i>She and Lin Yujing went to the welcome party.</i>

224
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:41,159
<i>Juan, don't worry. I'll post this news</i>

225
00:15:41,159 --> 00:15:43,440
<i>to that nonsense thread to clear your name.</i>

226
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:47,320
<i>Forget it. I'm afraid you'll make it worse.</i>

227
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:49,840
<i>Besides, that welcome party sounds fun.</i>

228
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:51,399
<i>Why don't we go take a look?</i>

229
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:53,120
<i>That's not the point!</i>

230
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:56,120
<i>He, you don't understand. It's urgent!</i>

231
00:15:57,679 --> 00:15:59,840
<i>It's not a big deal. Forget it.</i>

232
00:16:14,759 --> 00:16:18,279
<i>♪ Embrace you again ♪</i>

233
00:16:25,159 --> 00:16:26,960
How was our performance?

234
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,960
Awesome!

235
00:16:28,960 --> 00:16:30,559
If you join our guitar club,

236
00:16:30,559 --> 00:16:32,840
maybe you guys will be standing here next year.

237
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,840
- Really?
- You don't believe me?

238
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:38,560
No!

239
00:16:41,898 --> 00:16:43,616
<i>[Guitar Club]</i>

240
00:16:45,344 --> 00:16:49,240
Well, then. Does anyone want to come up
and be our lead singer?

241
00:16:51,639 --> 00:16:53,200
Yes! She will!

242
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:54,840
I-I won't sing.

243
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:57,080
I gave you the perfect makeup.
You have to sing.

244
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:59,480
Yeah! I want to hear What Kind of Man!
I'll send it to Shen Juan.

245
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:02,480
What Kind of Man!
I'll let Shen Juan hear you sing this song!

246
00:17:05,079 --> 00:17:06,960
Go! Go!

247
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:10,240
Come on! Sing a song!

248
00:17:11,799 --> 00:17:13,279
