00:35:18,039 --> 00:35:19,264
Thank you.

506
00:35:24,639 --> 00:35:26,199
Is there anything I can do now?

507
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:30,159
Where is your work badge?

508
00:35:30,159 --> 00:35:31,440
Haven't you completed the procedures yet?

509
00:35:32,440 --> 00:35:34,119
I forgot my ID today.

510
00:35:35,639 --> 00:35:36,960
If the procedures are not done,

511
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,400
you're not a staff member here.

512
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:39,920
I can't assign work to you.

513
00:35:39,920 --> 00:35:41,760
Rather than sitting here all day,

514
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:42,920
you might as well go back early.

515
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,719
But the HR said…

516
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:49,239
When you leave, please close the door for me.

517
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:51,456
Thanks.

518
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:08,760
Lin, I need a favor.

519
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:10,719
I forgot my ID card.

520
00:36:10,719 --> 00:36:11,880
Could you help me deliver it?

521
00:36:13,056 --> 00:36:14,079
Send me the address.

522
00:36:14,079 --> 00:36:15,519
<i>Okay, thank you!</i>

523
00:36:17,519 --> 00:36:19,360
<i>Let's have lunch together.</i>

524
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:22,272
<i>Okay.</i>

525
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:29,079
<i>Wait for me after class.
I'll come to find you.</i>

526
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:36,159
Mr. Fu, can you assign work to me now?

527
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:47,679
Okay, then you can help
sort out this class action case

528
00:36:47,679 --> 00:36:48,920
and deliver it to all parties today.

529
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:51,168
Okay.

530
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:12,119
Shen Juan, are you free? Let's talk.

531
00:37:17,039 --> 00:37:18,679
Shen Juan, I understand

532
00:37:18,679 --> 00:37:20,199
you won't tell me why you left,

533
00:37:20,199 --> 00:37:22,480
so I won't ask you again.

534
00:37:24,440 --> 00:37:26,159
I just want you to come back.

535
00:37:26,159 --> 00:37:28,639
The National University Games
will be held next March.

536
00:37:28,639 --> 00:37:31,480
Shen Juan, if you come back
and continue training, it's still not too late.

537
00:37:32,039 --> 00:37:35,199
Rong Huai, I've quit for four years.

538
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,960
Do you know

539
00:37:37,960 --> 00:37:39,424
what four years mean to an athlete?

540
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:42,840
You don't need to worry about this.

541
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:45,599
Xue from the provincial team
also gave up shooting midway.

542
00:37:45,599 --> 00:37:47,119
But after two years of training,

543
00:37:47,119 --> 00:37:49,559
he won a medal in the Provincial Sports Meet
the year before last.

544
00:37:50,559 --> 00:37:52,519
Medals are no longer important to me.

545
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:05,360
I can't accept it.

546
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:08,599
Shen Juan,
you clearly have talent and opportunity.

547
00:38:08,599 --> 00:38:10,360
You have the ability to reach the peak.

548
00:38:11,480 --> 00:38:13,119
How could you give up halfway up the mountain?

549
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:26,912
Rong Huai,

550
00:38:28,079 --> 00:38:30,079
there's no place for me up there.

551
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:32,880
Now I can only struggle
at the bottom of the mountain.

552
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:38,920
Shen Juan, wait a moment.

553
00:38:47,001 --> 00:38:48,320
<i>[Pucheng Junior Shooting Team
Prepares for National Championship]</i>

554
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:49,559
Do you remember?

555
00:38:49,559 --> 00:38:52,840
This was our assistant coach, Coach Lei.

556
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:54,239
Now he is the main coach of Pucheng University.

557
00:38:56,719 --> 00:38:59,039
If you ask him now,
there might still be a chance.

558
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:15,920
Shen Juan, please think about this, okay?

559
00:39:19,440 --> 00:39:20,960
The past is the past.

560
00:39:22,159 --> 00:39:23,199
Let's not mention it again.

561
00:39:42,559 --> 00:39:44,064
Let's go.

562
00:39:48,559 --> 00:39:51,440
I heard what you were saying just now.

563
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:12,239
When I was in the sixth grade
of elementary school,

564
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:14,000
I got into shooting

565
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,519
and met Rong Huai.

566
00:40:17,519 --> 00:40:18,960
He is two years younger than me.

567
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:20,960
We shared a dormitory.

568
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:23,559
The training during the day was pretty tough.

569
00:40:24,679 --> 00:40:25,800
When we got back in the evening,

570
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:27,239
he would hide in his blanket and cry.

571
00:40:29,639 --> 00:40:31,199
I could never get a good night's sleep.

572
00:40:32,559 --> 00:40:34,320
So I dragged him out of bed

573
00:40:34,960 --> 00:40:36,360
and took him to run around the sports field.

574
00:40:38,119 --> 00:40:39,239
And after that,

575
00:40:39,239 --> 00:40:41,360
he could immediately fall asleep
as soon as he lay down.

576
00:40:43,519 --> 00:40:45,119
What were you training for at the time?

577
00:40:45,119 --> 00:40:46,719
Rapid fire.

578
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,736
Why this?

579
00:40:49,599 --> 00:40:50,960
When I was a kid, the teacher said

580
00:40:52,119 --> 00:40:53,719
China's first gold medal

581
00:40:53,719 --> 00:40:55,159
was won in the shooting event

582
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:59,239
at the 1984 Los Angeles Olympics.

583
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:02,639
So, since childhood,

584
00:41:03,360 --> 00:41:05,199
I've always admired

585
00:41:05,199 --> 00:41:06,599
the champions who won glory for our country.

586
00:41:08,079 --> 00:41:10,800
I think their lives are incredibly cool.

587
00:41:15,639 --> 00:41:17,159
You're already pretty cool.

588
00:41:22,840 --> 00:41:24,920
When I was young, I was just a slacker.

589
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:27,639
I had no aspirations or dreams.

590
00:41:27,639 --> 00:41:29,000
It seemed like I was always

591
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:30,840
going through exams and studying.

592
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:34,039
My mom chose my high school,

593
00:41:34,039 --> 00:41:35,920
and she chose my college major.

594
00:41:36,719 --> 00:41:39,599
It's as if I've always been
walking the path she has laid out for me.

595
00:41:41,840 --> 00:41:42,920
I've never figured out

596
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:44,480
what I want to do in the future

597
00:41:45,159 --> 00:41:47,280
or what kind of person I can become.

598
00:41:49,960 --> 00:41:51,000
But you're different.

599
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:55,159
You have aspirations and dreams.

600
00:41:55,679 --> 00:41:57,480
And you know what you want.

601
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:02,880
So, no matter what happens,

602
00:42:04,679 --> 00:42:06,199
you should do it if you like it.

603
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:08,119
You should strive for what you want.

604
00:42:09,159 --> 00:42:10,320
No matter the outcome,

605
00:42:11,599 --> 00:42:14,400
don't be afraid and don't hide from it.

606
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:20,119
After all, you can do anything you want, right?

607
00:42:46,400 --> 00:42:49,159
<i>I secretly said I miss you.</i>

608
00:42:49,159 --> 00:42:51,519
<i>You gave me an incredibly brilliant world.</i>

609
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:55,079
<i>I'll give my daydreams to you.</i>

610
00:43:10,241 --> 00:43:14,785
<i>♫ Love sprouts in my palm ♫</i>

611
00:43:16,097 --> 00:43:19,937
<i>♫ Yet worried linger within my eyes ♫</i>

612
00:43:21,729 --> 00:43:26,305
<i>♫ Our story hasn't ended ♫</i>

613
00:43:27,233 --> 00:43:30,913
<i>♫ So where are we now ♫</i>

614
00:43:32,737 --> 00:43:38,401
<i>♫ I want to hug you so badly ♫</i>

615
00:43:38,401 --> 00:43:42,465
<i>♫ I want to become better with you ♫</i>

616
00:43:43,713 --> 00:43:48,577
<i>♫ The youth we shared ♫</i>

617
00:43:48,577 --> 00:43:54,625
<i>♫ Turned into a rainbow within my heart ♫</i>

618
00:43:55,137 --> 00:44:00,705
<i>♫ I really want to warm you ♫</i>

619
00:44:00,705 --> 00:44:02,593
<i>♫ I want to share with you ♫</i>

620
00:44:02,593 --> 00:44:07,265
<i>♫ The beauty of the world ♫</i>

621
00:44:08,149 --> 00:44:10,369
<i>♫ We promised ♫</i>

622
00:44:10,945 --> 00:44:16,641
<i>♫ To never be apart ♫</i>

623
00:44:17,377 --> 00:44:23,079
<i>♫ Do you want to hear me sing ♫</i>

624
00:44:23,079 --> 00:44:27,841
<i>♫ The wind chime swaying in my heart ♫</i>

625
00:44:28,385 --> 00:44:32,609
<i>♫ Is a wish ♫</i>

626
00:44:33,345 --> 00:44:39,233
<i>♫ I secretly made for you ♫</i>

627
00:44:39,777 --> 00:44:45,313
<i>♫ I want to plant ♫</i>

628
00:44:45,313 --> 00:44:47,201
<i>♫ A red maple forest ♫</i>

629
00:44:47,201 --> 00:44:51,809
<i>♫ To dye the whole mountain red ♫</i>

630
00:44:52,737 --> 00:44:54,977
<i>♫ The sky after the rain ♫</i>

631
00:44:55,617 --> 00:45:00,545
<i>♫ Was painted by our brilliant dreams ♫</i>

632
00:45:07,425 --> 00:45:12,193
<i>♫ Time is a flower of dream ♫</i>

633
00:45:13,025 --> 00:45:18,111
<i>♫ You've already collected it ♫</i>

634
00:45:19,041 --> 00:45:23,041
<i>♫ When we all become better ♫</i>

635
00:45:24,513 --> 00:45:28,641
<i>♫ We'll see the best of the world together ♫</i>
